Name: Corrupted Flesh
Description: A piece of corrupted flesh that has dropped from the corrupted. It has little use. Dark purple tendrils scorch the skin, wrapping around it like snakes devouring its prey

Name: Sharpened Fangs
Description: The fangs of a Jawworm. Some people have used it to sharpen their weapons and improve them but other than that, it has little use.

Name: Fangs of Eternity
Description: Shards of the cloak that the Servant of Memories wear. It feels... familier but you can't put a finger on it

Name: Shattered Stones
Description: Fractured parts of a Stone Serpant. There's nothing special about it. In fact, it looks like the same rocks you find around you... right?
